g Dostoevsky’s religious probing.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aLiterary Studies -- European. 4aLiterary Studies -- General Criticism and Theory. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Russian & Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476761340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767613423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767613/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles